snippet.title: I Made a 2D Party Game! [Sumo]
snippet.description:
Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2974140/Sumo/

Sumo is a 2D party game where you can play alone or with friends to knock each other out of the arena! Customize your character and unlock new customization options by fishing at the offline lake area.

This is very different content from the rest of this channel, but more animation is coming I swear.
